AUDIO: 'Hi there. I\'m excited today to showcase the new Alchemy agent template, which is made in collaboration with our partner Alchemy, one of the leading blockchain developer platforms. This agent template will allow you to spin up your very own Alchemy agent in'

[00:22] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'just a few clicks, and then let you explore and monitor wallets, assets, and then tokens all within a single out-of-the-box agent. To get started, we\'re going to go ahead'

[00:34] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and click on create your first agent. This will take us to the agent creation wizard. Here you can either customize your own agent setup or get started with an agent template from our marketplace.'

[00:47] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Since we\'re installing the Alchemy agent today, let\'s head on over to the agent marketplace. Here we can learn more about the agent,'

[01:01] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'what it can do, and what\'s required to set it up. So, let\'s go ahead and get started by clicking on the Alchemy agent. Here we can see that the agent has three'

[01:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'main features. So, the first we have wallet intelligence, and this is going to let you ask the agent about any wallet and get a full multi-chain profile on that wallet. So, you can see things like token balances, NFT'

[01:25] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'holdings, transfers, and really get a full profile picture of what that wallet looks like across all Alchemy supported chains. Next, we\'re going to have smart money'

[01:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'tracking. So, this is going to let you ask your agent to set up a watch so that you can monitor any wallet across any network for any asset transfers, acquisitions, or new positions that wallet might be taking.'

[01:50] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'When something happens, you get alerted on the channel of your choosing. And lastly, we have the token and NFT price monitoring tool. So, if you have specific assets that you care deeply about, you can set up an automated tool'

[02:03] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that\'s going to watch these assets and alert you to any huge swings in those prices. You can run this on 15-minute intervals, 1-minute intervals, an hour. It\'s really up to you. And then you can'

[02:15] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'also set thresholds so that you can choose whether you want to get alerted on, say, 5% swings or anything down to a fraction of a percent. Really, the customization is up to you. Okay.'

